The majority of demonstrations were peaceful, although a [[Vista, California]] rally took a violent turn at day's end when crowds began throwing rocks and bottles at sheriff's deputies. There were also two arrests made at a demonstration in Los Angeles's [[MacArthur Park]].<ref>{{cite news 
